Meteo Radar is perfect for families planning weekends or people doing outdoor activities. Our app helps you plan your day so that the weather doesn’t interfere with any of your daily activities. Detailed hourly forecast for everyday, 14-day forecast, and a map showing the weather in real-time. The weather will no longer surprise you, you will always know what to wear, prepare for weekends, and whether you need to take an umbrella today.
Whether you are planning a vacation, engaging in your favorite outdoor activity, or you just need to know if it will be rainy this weekend, Meteo Radar provides you with the most accurate weather forecast around using local data from NOAA (National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration).
Key features:
Today’s Min, Max, and “Feels Like” temperature to know what is coming for you today;
Detailed info for a day - Drill down and explore temperature, precipitation, humidity, UV-index, pressure, and more day by day;
7-day forecast with 1-hour step - to plan weekends and activities with confidence;
Realtime radar - Interactive radar shows you the direction and speed of the wind, where is rainy, and where the storms are to keep you safe (over 20 layers available).
Premium features:
14-day forecasts with 1-hour step;
Daily weather reports with forecasts and recommendations;
Adjustable weather layouts for radar (20+ layouts).
